# RoboVacuumDDPG — environment variable template.
# Copy to `.env` (git-ignored) and fill if/when needed. The project makes NO
# external API calls at runtime (training is local on HouseExpo maps), so no
# secrets are required for the core pipeline. Listed for completeness / future use.

# Optional: override the HouseExpo dataset location if pre-downloaded.
# HOUSEEXPO_DIR=/path/to/HouseExpo

# Optional: pin a CPU/GPU device for training.
# TORCH_DEVICE=cpu
